Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
I think it is not a bad thing for freshmen to live on campus. Just leaving high school, the freshmen will face to a completedly different environment, with lots of tempts. It is good for them to stay within campus and focus on study instead of party. Also it is easier in campus for students to take care of each other.